 have a common language.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Features:</h3>\r\n<p>Two interpretation modes are available: On-site Interpretation and In-Call Interpretation. Users can connect to interpreters via voice call and transmit video and photos anytime, anywhere. With human translation, as opposed to machine translation, ambiguity in meaning is avoided, giving you a more accurate translation.</p><br>\r\n','About UsYesPoYour assistant, there when you need it!What?YesPo provides an online human interpreting service platform with the principal aim of solving language-barrier problems in all domains.Why?It is important that people can understand each other, exchange information and ideas even they do not have a common language.Features:Two interpretation modes are available: On-site Interpretation and In-Call Interpretation. Users can connect to interpreters via voice call and transmit video and photos anytime, anywhere. With human translation, as opposed to machine translation, ambiguity in meaning is avoided, giving you a more accurate translation.','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7444,'A58BF9A3FE580102D5C164D1BEE128F4','A52E2DEED45DB237FE8FEE5ABADA7D08','en','\r\n	<h2 align=\"center\">Contact Us</h2>\r\n	<p align=\"center\" class=\"textva\">We\'re an energetic team</p>\r\n	<div class=\"line\"></div>\r\n	<p align=\"center\" class=\"textvb\">Should you have any enquiries, <br>please email us: <a href=\"mailto:support@yespo.com\">support@yespo.com</a> <br>or drop us a message!</p>\r\n','Contact UsWe\'re an energetic teamShould you have any enquiries, please email us: support@yespo.com or drop us a message!','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7445,'8F4A56CD999202210350F24D7E8BC3CE','7144CF4FA045F81AC2CFC1BC843E2CC9','en','support@yespo.com','support@yespo.com','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7446,'27EDEDB9651DC5071D727C5764B592F6','378D9BE8DAE4EC7D9BB2B796B8D2ABA5','en','Name','Name','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7447,'53E428C2843B542CB742EA40EBB31695','01B6