ect either “Reset via login email” or “Reset via phone number”. Note: The email address and telephone number must have been verified in order to retrieve your password using this method.</p>\r\n		<p>2. If the email address and telephone number has not yet been verified, please <a href=\"//m.yespo.com/index/contact\">contact us</a>.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	\r\n	<li>\r\n		<h3>How do I change the language of the app? </h3>\r\n		<p>Open the YesPo app. In the menu bar, select Me > Settings > Language and select your desired language.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	\r\n	<li>\r\n		<h3>Can I connect to an interpreter at any time?</h3>\r\n		<p>Yes, our interpreters are online 24 hours a day, 365 days a year.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	\r\n	<li>\r\n		<h3>Is my personal information and the content of my interpretation kept confidential?</h3>\r\n		<p>All our interpreters have signed a confidentiality agreement with YesPo, which states that all information pertaining to YesPo’s interpreting work remains strictly confidential. We regularly monitor the interpretation calls and sometimes record the calls for quality assurance purposes. However, we guarantee that the recordings and the contents of your conversations to any third party will not be disclosed without your authorization.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	\r\n	<li>\r\n		<h3>What is the difference between “on-site interpretation” and “in-call interpretation”?</h3>\r\n		<p>“On-site interpretation” is interpretation needed at the scene. After connecting to an interpreter via voice call, the user can transmit video and send photos if needed, or turn on loudspeaker for interpretation of conversations between individuals present at the scene. “In-call interpretation” is provided in a three-way call mode, where the interpreter translates the conversation for two users via voice call.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','FAQGeneral questionsWhat is YesPo?YesPo is a platform which provides human online interpretation services. Use YesPo to connect to an interpreter anytime, anywhere, solving all your language problems. Find out moreHow do I become a YesPo user?Users can register as a user using YesPo’s mobile app. After entering your telephone number and email address, you will receive a verification code via SMS, which you will need to complete registration. You can contact us if you encounter any problems.I tried registering but I get a message saying that my email address and telephone number has already been used, what should I do?As this email address has previously been used for registration, you cannot re-use this information to register as a new user. You can retrieve this information as follows:1. If the email address and telephone number has already been verified, tap on “Forgot Password” and select either “Reset via login email” or “Reset via phone number”. Note: The email address and telephone number must have been verified in order to retrieve your password using this method.2. If the email address and telephone number has not yet been verified, please contact us.How do I change the language of the app? Open the YesPo app. In the menu bar, select Me > Settings > Language and select your desired language.Can I connect to an interpreter at any time?Yes, our interpreters are online 24 hours a day, 365 days a year.Is my personal information and the content of my interpretation kept confidential?All our interpreters have signed a confidentiality agreement with YesPo, which states that all information pertaining to YesPo’s interpreting work remains strictly confidential. We regularly monitor the interpretation calls and sometimes record the calls for quality assurance purposes. However, we guarantee that the recordings and the contents of your conversations to any third party will not be disclosed without your authorization.What is the difference between “on-site interpretation” and “in-call interpretation”?“On-site interpretation” is interpretation needed at the scene. After connecting to an interpreter via voice call, the user can transmit video and send photos if needed, or turn on loudspeaker for interpretation of conversations between individuals present at the scene. “In-call interpretation” is provided in a three-way call mode, where the interpreter translates the conversation for two users via voice call.','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7453,'FBFF67DF9592A46AA653B2AD138A8404','53EBAE4A7A2F525A1E03D284F6D6A32E','en','YESPO','YESPO','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7454,'74B8F0D389A54442E5114EB5542C1EC1','F3F4C813FB3073A69F57B7726CC350C1','en','verification code','verification code','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7455,'5CF93BFDD80B122483B31D47B9FB4C14','101F725AAF5D8AFF245DA965625D02B0','en','The World\'s Top Interpreting Platform','The World\'s Top Interpreting Platform','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7456,'9F42153363C2476CC1AC4B6E7436C7CC','A5F9AB1C16BDFD7E2EEF1874464C4F17','en','YESPO','YESPO','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7457,'2C1F5B809042F7E04EB408AA680B81B2','75F0807DE1A3EAE7C2107EE475AAB0B6','en','Call interpreter when at the scene','Call interpreter when at the scene','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7458,'214A1DA194D71141AD5B3857DB8DC137','1913197005802B459338F752E986406F','en','In-call Interpretation','In-call Interpretation','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7459,'BFC20C9531D6B9CD216855B47ED730F4','88419A5381C8B0714D3B20C2C7673AB4','en','Call interpreter and third party','Call interpreter and third party','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7460,'A4344946147937BF4D8C23F2014219D0','DF75AAB349D164EB4860D8440B536C35','en','Download Free','Download Free','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7461,'8C4A9E79138C5AAB2D3DD468B5212F38','547C9C8CE2174023C83B795EF38D2AC2','en','On-site Interpretation','On-site Interpretation','',1,'Colin Kuan (SF578)',1464828270),(7462,'FABD699E41EE584E7544C0D6CB40F8DC','EB3C2DB20AC98012A74F4BF4DCA62464','en','Distanceless! Convenient! All-round!','Distanceless! Convenient! All-round!','',1,'Colin Kuan